𝐈𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐚𝐧 + 𝐀𝐮𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐞 Burger = ?⁣
⁣
Decided to 𝘣𝘶𝘳𝘨𝘦𝘳𝘪𝘻𝘦𝘥 one 𝐄𝐏𝐈𝐂 𝐟𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧 burger during this stay home times with a combination of distinct flavors ! ⁣
⁣
Consisting between those sesame shiny buns , a warm sunny side up egg usually used in aussie burger with 𝘥𝘳𝘪𝘱𝘱𝘪𝘯 𝘺𝘰𝘭𝘬𝘺𝘯𝘦𝘴𝘴 , slices of tomatoes🍅 , cheese🧀.. ⁣
adding an italian crunch with truffle parmesan cheese 𝘱𝘰𝘵𝘢𝘵𝘰 𝘤𝘩𝘪𝘱𝘴 from @aromatruffle..⁣🍄
⁣
Shitake mushrooms🍄 , seaweed , sadia prime beef burger patties & fresh butterhead lettuce 🥬,⁣
⁣
For da sauce , i used 𝘋𝘦 𝘕𝘪𝘨𝘳𝘪𝘴 𝘐𝘵𝘢𝘭𝘪𝘢𝘯 𝘉𝘉𝘘 𝘚𝘢𝘶𝘤𝘦 & 𝘒𝘦𝘸𝘱𝘪𝘦 𝘔𝘢𝘺𝘰 ,⁣💯
⁣
Do u Love dem burgers dripppin with sauce?? I do! cheers! 🍻
